        <!-- Cards grid -->
        <div class="tst-block--body">

            <!-- Card 1 -->
            <div class="tst-card">
                <div class="tst-card__content">
                    <div class="filled-ratingstar">
                        <img src="assets/reviewPlatform-icons/FilledRatingStars.svg" alt="Five-star rating">
                    </div>
                    <p class="review-platform-default">(Original) Estamos encantado con Optimun como nuestro nuevo
                        procesamiento, las transacciones son mas claras para nosotros y nuestros clientes. Paul y
                        Eddie son excelentes para aclarar cualquier duda. <em>(Translated by Google) We're delighted
                            with Optimum as our new processing solution; transactions are much clearer for both us
                            and
                            our customers. Paul and Eddie are excellent at answering any questions.</em></p>
                </div>
                <div class="tst-card__footer">
                    <div class="tst-card__avatar">
                        <img src="assets/reviewersAvatar/GAMASERVICES USA.png" alt="GAMASERVICES USA">
                        <div class="review-source-logo"><img
                                src="assets/reviewPlatform-icons/review-source-Google-Ico.png"
                                alt="Google review source"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tst-card__reviewer">
                        <span class="tst-card__name">GAMASERVICES USA</span>
                        <span class="tst-card__date">Oct 31, 2025</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 2 -->
            <div class="tst-card">
                <div class="tst-card__content">
                    <div class="filled-ratingstar filled-ratingstar--facebook">
                        <img class="fb-recommend-star" src="assets/reviewPlatform-icons/fbRecommendsIcon.svg"
                            alt="Facebook recommends">
                        <span class="filled-ratingstar__label__fromFacebook">Recommends</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="review-platform-default">I'm a small business owner and I was cautious about leaving
                        PNC
                        card processing. I was with them for a long time. PNC kept raising processing fees year
                        after
                        year. I'm so glad I spoke to Paul at Optimum Payment Solutions. He explained things very
                        well
                        and made my switch quick and easy. I only wish I switched years ago!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tst-card__footer">
                    <div class="tst-card__avatar">
                        <img src="assets/reviewersAvatar/DavidYongChoi.webp" alt="David Yong Choi">
                        <div class="review-source-logo"><img
                                src="assets/reviewPlatform-icons/review-source-Facebook-Ico.png"
                                alt="Facebook review source"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tst-card__reviewer">
                        <span class="tst-card__name">David Yong Choi</span>
                        <span class="tst-card__date">Sep 17, 2024</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 3 -->
            <div class="tst-card">
                <div class="tst-card__content">
                    <div class="filled-ratingstar">
                        <img src="assets/reviewPlatform-icons/FilledRatingStars.svg" alt="Five-star rating">
                    </div>
                    <p class="review-platform-default">Had been with PNC for credit card processing, since our
                        business started taking cards summer of 2015. The fees that we paid for accepting cards kept
                        rising, and there were several times when PNC did not even bother to respond to many of my
                        questions over the last 2 years. That included when we got a new credit card machine, and I
                        had a question about its use. I had questions BEFORE I signed a renewal contract, and those
                        were answered immediately. Once the contract was signed and I had a question about the
                        machine's operation, THEN PNC was nowhere to be found. VERY disappointing. Enter Paul with
                        Optimum Payment Solutions. Having worked with him before, I was excited to meet with him,
                        since he had exceeded all expectations that time as well. Paul answered ALL of my questions
                        about this program. I want to know Pros AND Cons of anything new, and Paul was very open
                        about
                        everything. Paul's phone and email responses to my questions and comments over the last
                        several
                        weeks have either been immediate, or VERY soon after, including his answering of my emails
                        later into the evenings, so he stays right on top of his clients and their needs. THIS is
                        what we have been missing for a while now. We got the machine that suits the exact needs of
                        our business, with no-nonsense fees that are easy for every customer to see RIGHT on their
                        receipt! All of our employees love this, and have been very happy over the last few weeks
                        over
                        the ease of using the machine, and how simple it was to transition. I had also been wanting
                        to
                        begin accepting EBT cards for a while, and had been doing research on navigating the waters
                        of
                        going through the government application process, and then getting a machine that would be
                        set
                        up to accept those cards as well. While Paul was in our business explaining how his payment
                        solutions worked, he went online with me, and walked me through the entire process and
                        helped
                        me to answer all questions correctly to COMPLETE the EBT application process. It all took
                        about 10 to 15 minutes total, whereas me doing it by myself, unfamiliar with everything,
                        would
                        have taken a MUCH longer amount of time. That was not even something that Paul was required
                        to
                        do, but this is a prime example of someone going way out of their way and bending over
                        backwards to ensure the best service for his customers. I am thrilled that we switched, and
                        with Paul's help, it was SO much easier than I thought it was going to be. 10 / 5 stars,
                        really. Paul with Optimum Payment Solutions has my business because he EARNED it.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tst-card__footer">
                    <div class="tst-card__avatar tst-card__avatar--dark">
                        <span class="tst-card__avatar--initials">KM</span>
                        <div class="review-source-logo"><img
                                src="assets/reviewPlatform-icons/review-source-Optimum-Ico.png"
                                alt="Optimum review source"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tst-card__reviewer">
                        <span class="tst-card__name">Karen Muth</span>
                        <span class="tst-card__date">Oct 26, 2021</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 4 -->
            <div class="tst-card">
                <div class="tst-card__content">
                    <div class="filled-ratingstar">
                        <img src="assets/reviewPlatform-icons/FilledRatingStars.svg" alt="Five-star rating">
                    </div>
                    <p class="review-platform-default">Paul has handled our credit card payments since our first day
                        in
                        business. Setup was easy and fast. Highly recommend.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tst-card__footer">
                    <div class="tst-card__avatar">
